attributionInfo.brokerName: THE REAL ESTATE CENTER OF NEW BERN, INC
THE REAL ESTATE CENTER OF NEW BERN, INC

data.description: *** UPDATE ***Worried about the current market and interest rates? Do you qualify for a VA Loan? Look no further!Buyers may be able to assume the current VA Loan at 3.5% interest and approximately $260,000 balance.*** UPDATE ***Stunning home located in the River Bluffs community. Gleaming hardwood floors that guide you through the open-concept living space, which is accentuated by a wall of windows and vaulted ceiling. The kitchen features exquisite granite countertops, custom cabinetry, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Enjoy Holiday entertaining in the formal dining room made for special gatherings. Retire to the spacious Master Bedroom, complete with a walk-in closet and a private en-suite bath. Additionally, there's a versatile bonus room that can easily be transformed into a fourth bedroom, a creative craft room, home office or a cozy, home gym, or entertainment room. Modern conveniences, include an energy-efficient Rinnai water heater and zoned natural gas heating to keep you comfortable year-round. Fall in love with the expansive back deck or the screened porch, perfect for enjoying your mornings or evenings. You'll also appreciate the above-ground pool and the serene views of your private fenced backyard, creating an oasis of relaxation. Two-car garage and an impressive driveway with and abundance of parking!
